column16: Coco Crisp singles on a soft line drive to center fielder Brandon Inge.    Kevin Youkilis scores.
J.  D.   Drew out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Brandon Inge.    Jacoby Ellsbury scores.
Kevin Youkilis hits a ground-rule double (3) on a fly ball down the right-field line.   Dustin Pedroia scores.    David Ortiz scores.    Jacoby Ellsbury to 3rd.
Jacoby Ellsbury walks.    Dustin Pedroia to 3rd.    David Ortiz to 2nd.
David Ortiz walks.    Dustin Pedroia to 2nd.
Dustin Pedroia singles on a line drive to right fielder Magglio Ordonez.
Julio Lugo grounds out, third baseman Miguel Cabrera to first baseman Carlos Guillen.
Juan Uribe doubles (2) on a line drive to right fielder Magglio Ordonez.    Joe Crede to 3rd.
Joe Crede singles on a fly ball to center fielder Clete Thomas.    Carlos Quentin scores.
Carlos Quentin triples (1) on a fly ball to center fielder Clete Thomas.    Orlando Cabrera scores.    Paul Konerko scores.    A.  J.   Pierzynski scores.
Yorman Bazardo intentionally walks A.  J.   Pierzynski.
Jermaine Dye grounds out, pitcher Yorman Bazardo to first baseman Carlos Guillen.    Orlando Cabrera to 3rd.    Paul Konerko to 2nd.
Paul Konerko singles on a ground ball to left fielder Marcus Thames.    Orlando Cabrera to 2nd.
Alexei Ramirez flies out to left fielder Marcus Thames.
Tony Pena grounds out, pitcher Yorman Bazardo to first baseman Carlos Guillen.
John Buck strikes out swinging and Ross Gload caught stealing 2nd, catcher Ivan Rodriguez to second baseman Placido Polanco.
